%%{ init: { 'theme': 'dark' } }%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 👤 User
    participant FE as Frontend (React)
    participant BE as Backend (FastAPI)
    participant STT as Whisper API
    participant LLM as GPT-4o
    participant BANK as Banking Service
    participant TTS as OpenAI TTS
    participant REDIS as Redis

    U->>+FE: Press & hold mic button
    FE->>FE: navigator.mediaDevices.getUserMedia
    FE->>FE: MediaRecorder.start()

    U->>-FE: Release mic button
    FE->>FE: MediaRecorder.stop()
    FE->>FE: audioChunks → Blob

    FE->>+BE: POST /api/v1/conversation/turn<br/>multipart: audio.webm + session_id

    BE->>+STT: audio_bytes
    STT->>-BE: transcript: "ما رصيدي؟"<br/>language: "ar"
    Note over BE: timer.stt recorded

    BE->>+REDIS: GET session:{session_id}
    REDIS->>-BE: turns: [...last 10]
    Note over BE: session_store.get_recent_turns_dict()

    BE->>+LLM: user_transcript + history + system_prompt
    LLM->>-BE: tool_calls: [get_account_balance]
    Note over BE: timer.llm recorded

    loop For each tool call
        BE->>+BANK: execute_tool("get_account_balance", {})
        BANK->>-BE: {accounts: [...], customer_name: "Hazem Taha"}
    end

    BE->>+LLM: tool_results → second LLM call
    LLM->>-BE: "رصيدك: حساب التوفير 38,200 BHD،<br/>الحساب الجاري 12,450 BHD"
    Note over BE: second LLM call included in timer.llm

    BE->>+TTS: response_text
    TTS->>-BE: audio_bytes (MP3)
    Note over BE: timer.tts recorded

    BE->>REDIS: APPEND turns (user + assistant)
    Note over BE: session ttl refreshed

    BE->>-FE: {<br/>  transcript: "ما رصيدي؟",<br/>  assistant_text: "...",<br/>  audio_url: "/api/v1/audio/{turn_id}",<br/>  latency_ms: {stt, llm, tools, tts, total}<br/>}

    FE->>+FE: Play audio response
    FE->>FE: Update transcript + latency panel
    FE->>-U: Show response bubble

    Note over U,FE: Total time: 1.5–2.5s on typical laptop + good connection